      <div xml:id="Aink8-kilavi">
        <p type="edition"> ituvumatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink8">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>          vāḻi yātaṉ vāḻi yaviṉi</l>
<l>          yaracumuṟai ceyka kaḷavil lākuka</l>
<l>          veṉavēṭ ṭōḷē yāyē yāmē</l>
<l>          yalaṅkuciṉai māat taṇimayi lirukkum</l>
<l>          pūkkaña lūraṉ cūḷivaṇ	</l>
<l>          vāyppa tāka veṉavēṭ ṭēmē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>          'May Ātaṉ prosper, may Aviṉi prosper.</l>
<l>          Let the king do justice, let there be no theft,'</l>
<l>          thus wants our mother. We:</l>
<l>          'The oath of the man from a village dense with flowers,</l>
<l>          where ornate peacocks perch in mango trees with swaying branches,</l>
<l>          let it be successful here,' thus we want.</l>
          


        </lg>
      </div>
